<BR>
One last note to people that use the phrasiology that is shawn below (ie. n00bz, etc.)Do you realize how ridiculous that sounds? Do you? EVERYONE was a newbie once...so were you, so stfu and be a decent person for a freaking change, its cause of people like you that the &quot;ideal raid&quot; would never work. Go be &quot;uber&quot; somewhere else on your own time, and let the people that actually want to play have fun and get something accomplished (and no, sitting in chat for 4 hours because some 12 year old uber wont shut up about loot is NOT fun)<BR>
<BR>
Sorry if i seemed to belittle your post Yap, but while thought out well, it seemed a bit demeaning, my prior one was just a little rib and just the way I am, we rogues have quite the personality. Anyone else who made it this far, thanks for paying attention to my little rant, and to the inevitable 12 year old idiot that is going to flame and call me a n00b, methinks, that perhaps it is you that are the newbie, and figure that by calling someone else a newbie and using ridiculous typing methods to do it that you will somehow get the acceptance on everlore that you are SORELY lacking in real life.<BR>
<BR>
Your hero and mine,<BR>
Rei.<BR>
